information)\n    * [Management Team](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/management-team)\n    * [Contacts](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/contacts)\n    * [FAQ](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/faq)\n  * [IR Calendar](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/ir-calendar)\n  * [Financial Info](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information)\n    * [Financial Results](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information/financial-results)\n    * [Income Statement](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information/income-statement)\n    * [Balance Sheet](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information/balance-sheet)\n    * [Cash Flow](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information/cash-flow)\n  * [Stock Data](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data)\n    * [Quote](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data/quote)\n    * [Charts](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data/charts)\n    * [Historical Data](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data/historical-data)\n    * [Analyst Coverage](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data/analyst-coverage)\n  * [SEC Filings](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings)\n    * [All SEC Filings](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings/all-sec-filings)\n    * [Annual Reports](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings/annual-reports)\n    * [Quarterly Reports](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings/quarterly-reports)\n    * [Section 16 Filings](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings/section-16-filings)\n  * [Governance](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance)\n    * [Board of Directors](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance/board-of-directors)\n    * [Board Committees](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance/board-committees)\n    * [Governance Documents](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance/governance-documents)\n    * [Board Diversity](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance/board-diversity)\n\n\n  * ### Company Info\n  * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information)\n  * [Management Team](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/management-team)\n  * [Contacts](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/contacts)\n  * [FAQ](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information/faq)\n\n\n## Company Profile\nWith its proprietary technology that combines high performance compound semiconductor nanomaterials with mass market silicon manufacturing, Aeluma is developing novel devices for sensors and communications. The Company has pioneered a technique to enable volume scaling and low cost without sacrificing performance. Aeluma is developing a streamlined business model from its headquarters in Goleta, California that has a state-of-the-art manufacturing cleanroom.\n## Industry Classifications\n**Sector:**  \nTechnology\n**Industry:**  \nSemiconductor\n**NAICS:**  \nResearch and Development in the Physical, Engineering, and Life Sciences (except Nanotechnology and Biotechnology) (541715)\n**SIC:**  \nSemiconductors and Related Devices (3674)\n## Contact Information\n**Investor Relations**  \nFinancial Profiles, Inc.  \nir@aeluma.com  \n\nMoira Conlon  \nT: 310-478-2700  \n\nAlex Villalta  \nT: 310-622-8227  \n\n**Company Contact**  \nAeluma, Inc.  \n27 Castilian Dr.  \nGoleta, CA 93117   \nUnited States   \nT: 805-351-2707   \ninfo@aeluma.com\n  * [ ![Visit us on LinkedIn](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21216/icon/icon-linkedin.svg) ](https://www.linkedin.com/company/aeluma \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on X](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21317/icon/icon-x-twitter.svg) ](https://x.com/Aeluma_Inc \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on Instagram](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21316/icon/icon-instagram.svg) ](https://www.instagram.com/aeluma.inc/ \"Opens in a new window\")\n\n\n\u00a9[Aeluma, Inc.](https://www.aeluma.com/) All Rights Reserved. \n[Privacy Policy](https://www.aeluma.com/privacy-policy) [Disclaimer](https://www.aeluma.com/disclaimer) [Sitemap](https://www.aeluma.com/sitemap)\n",
